  <brief_title>Circulating Tumor Cells (CTCs) in Advanced Gastric Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prediction of Recurrence in Advanced Gastric Cancer After Radical Resection by Circulating Tumor Cells （CTCs）</official_title>
  <sponsors>
