  <source>Peking University</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To assess the predictive value of circulating tumor cells (CTCs) for recurrence of advanced
      gastric cancer after radical resection.

      To identify the relationship between the detection of circulation tumor cells and recurrence
      patterns of gastric cancer after radical resection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
